// system-binds.md §6.4: a capability injection written directly inside a
// comptime-folded root has no bind in scope (comptime folding runs before
// the checker's bind-scope pass exists) — denied at the injection site,
// before any call could reach the ordinary hermetic-comptime sys* deny.
use std::IEnv;
comptime int N = (inject IEnv).args().length();
console.writeln(N);
